column4: REFILE-Tesla delivers Model X electric SUV to take on luxury carmakers
column5: FREMONT  Calif.  Sept 29 Tesla Motors  delivered the first of its long-awaited Model X electric sports-utility vehicles on Tuesday  a product investors are counting on to make the pioneering company profitable after years of losses.
